response.overview: Remember the Love Generation? Well the 60's are back with the next generation of hot, open-minded, easy-lovin' hotties. And of course, our very own Phil Varone found them, right in Hot-Lanta! Join Phil's 100% Real Swingers as he meets a group called the "Juniper Generation" affectionately named after the beautiful Addie Juniper, "Ring Leader" of wild swing parties that you won't soon forget. Think of it as The Real Swingers of Atlanta...but you'll never find it on cable TV!
response.title: 100% Real Teen Swingers: Atlanta
